# Contact / Request Demo form integration.
#
# The contact form posts to /api/contact, which forwards to this Formspree
# endpoint. Create a form at https://formspree.io pointed at
# hello@persimmon-clinical.com and paste the endpoint URL here.
#
# If this is left unset, the form transparently falls back to a mailto: link,
# so nothing breaks on deploy.
FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT=
